title: The Tudors - Season 3 - Opening Intro
author: GotPilot
comment: There is something so charming in this moment 0:19, when he stands up. The real king😍
What a Fine song this is! The synths are fierce! 👑
I love Annabelle Wallis’s portrayal of Jane

The original Game Of Thrones and to this day The Tudor’s will always come first to me. 

I love this show so much. It was so well written and Jonathan Rhys Meyers you just love to hate him.
The show sort of dipped in my opinion after the death of Anne Boleyn but I get that it’s for historical accuracy so you can’t be angry with the writers for just writing what happened lol.
